<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Responsive CSS3 Showcase</title>
    <!-- External Fonts & Icons -->
    <link href="https://googleapis.com" rel="stylesheet">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.0.0/css/all.min.css">
    
    <style>
        :root {
            --primary: #6c5ce7;
            --dark: #2d3436;
            --light: #f9f9f9;
        }

        * { margin: 0; padding: 0; box-sizing: border-box; }

        body {
            font-family: 'Poppins', sans-serif;
            background: var(--light);
            color: var(--dark);
        }

        header {
            height: 40vh;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #6c5ce7, #a29bfe);
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            color: white;
            animation: fadeIn 1.5s ease-in; /* CSS3 Animation */
        }

        @keyframes fadeIn {
            from { opacity: 0; }
            to { opacity: 1; }
        }

        .container {
            max-width: 1100px;
            margin: -50px auto 50px;
            padding: 0 20px;
        }

        /* Multiple Columns Feature */
        .content-box {
            background: white;
            padding: 40px;
            border-radius: 15px;
            column-count: 2; /* CSS3 Columns */
            column-gap: 40px;
            box-shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
        }

        /* Icons & Transformations */
        .feature-grid {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(200px, 1fr));
            gap: 20px;
            margin-top: 30px;
        }

        .card {
            background: white;
            padding: 20px;
            text-align: center;
            transition: transform 0.3s ease; /* Smooth transition */
            border-radius: 10px;
        }

        .card:hover {
            transform: translateY(-10px) scale(1.05); /* CSS3 Transform */
        }

        /* Responsive Breakpoints */
        @media (max-width: 768px) {
            .content-box { column-count: 1; }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <header>
        <h1 style="font-family: 'Playfair Display'; font-size: 3rem;">Creative Design</h1>
        <p>Built with pure CSS3</p>
    </header>

    <div class="container">
        <div class="content-box">
            <h2>Modern Layouts</h2>
            <p>This text is split into multiple columns using CSS3 <code>column-count</code>. It behaves like a newspaper layout but remains fully responsive on smaller devices.</p>
            <p>By using <code>transition</code> and <code>transform</code>, we add life to static elements without needing heavy JavaScript.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="feature-grid">
            <div class="card"><i class="fas fa-bolt"></i><h3>Fast</h3></div>
            <div class="card"><i class="fas fa-layer-group"></i><h3>Modern</h3></div>
            <div class="card"><i class="fas fa-mobile-alt"></i><h3>Responsive</h3></div>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
